'''JU-9 Juggernaut War Droid''' were types of [[Juggernaut war droid]]s used by [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Vrox]]. One such [[Droid/Legends|droid]] was used to attempt to slow down the forces of the [[Republican Army]] so that Vrox could escape the [[Battle of Mandalore (pre-Naboo)|Battle of Mandalore]].<ref name="BFM">{{ChallengeCite|58|Battle for Mandalore}}</ref>

